rooms_desc ({"You are at the end of a path in a large canyon.\nTowering walls of brown rock and granite loom on\nall three sides of you. You see little piles of\nrubble at the foots of the cliffs. Except for a \nfew field mice and a lizard or two, this place\ndoesnt look like too many have been here. All\nlooks in place except for a steel door to the north\nwith a small terminal along side of it. There is\na sign painted on the door.\n","You enter this room and the door behind you\npounds shut. You start to feel a change in the\nair around you. As a series of gasses fill the\nroom, you feel refreshed. Just then, a door to\nthe west opens. You look around the room and see\nsmall holes with spouts extending from them.\nOther than that, the room is empty.\n","In this room, you see hundreds of people,\ngoing to and fro, about their business.\nThere is a feeling of friendliness in the\nair here. You notice the Ambassador of the\ncolony smiling in your direction. As you\nlook around, you see chairs, couches, and\nstools for your comfort. There are food\nand drink terminals along the walls. You\nseem to feel at home here.\n","In this room, there are four large couches\nthat are in the form of a square. In the center\nof the 'square', there is a large table.\nThis table serves as an entertainment center\nfor those who just feel like taking a break\nfrom it all. The table is voice activated,\nso all that is needed is a word and you can \nwatch your favorite movie or television show.\nIf not, you can just sit down and talk. There\nare more terminals along the walls. There is \na sign above the north door.\n",0,0,0,0,0,0,})
